"dotnet new xunit -n DevSpot.Tests"

Add test project to your project:
"dotnet sln ASP.NET.sln add DevSpot.Tests/DevSpot.Tests.csproj"

Add project reference:
"dotnet add DevSpot.Tests/DevSpot.Tests.csproj reference DevSpot/DevSpot.csproj"

"dotnet sln ASP.NET.sln list"

In memory db:
"dotnet add DevSpot.Tests package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.InMemory"

[FACT] attribute to a function specifies that it shd be run by the test runner.